(1785, 2, '2016-03-08 22:10:19', '2016-03-08 21:10:19', '<h3>Jane &amp; Robert - Crillon Le Brave</h3>\r\n<div>Jeannette Riahi (Janet &amp; Co) looks after our house in Crillon le Brave for us, and we are very pleased with the service she offers.</div>\r\n<div> She prepares the house before we arrive, and closes it down after we have left. She also regularly checks on the house when we are away. Jeannette supervises any workmen that need to work on the house in our absence. Jeannette also offers us a cleaning service when we are in Crillon le Brave, and we have always been very pleased with the quality of her work.</div>\r\n<div>We have been loyal clients of Jeannette’s for a number of years, and would highly recommend her services.</div>', 'Témoignage de Jane & Robert - GRANDE BRETAGNE - Mars 2016', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'temoignage-de-jane-et-robert', '', '', '2021-02-20 11:47:34', '2021-02-20 10:47:34', '', 0, 'http://janet-and-co.fr/?post_type=dt_testimonials&#038;p=1785', 0, 'dt_testimonials', '', 0),
