(2115, 2, '2022-08-04 17:29:38', '2022-08-04 16:29:38', '<h3>Peter - Bedoin</h3>\r\nI have been so fortunate to collaborate with Janet &amp;Co for close to two years by now. Up until then i tired to manage our property from a distance. However, it was difficult to do all the things needed owning a house, e.g. check up on the health of the House, meter readings, and empty the post box from afar. Hence, I felt really lucky finding Janet &amp;Co. They took over the concierge role and initially visited the house every months, but has since then assisted on small and large tasks.One of the largest identifying and working with local craftsmen. They do an excellent job obtaining quotations and managing the process.', 'Témoignage de Peter - DANEMARK - Août 2022', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'temoignage-de-peter-danemark-juillet-2022', '', '', '2022-08-04 17:39:56', '2022-08-04 16:39:56', '', 0, 'http://janet-and-co.fr/?post_type=dt_testimonials&#038;p=2115', 0, 'dt_testimonials', '', 0),
